## Running the Application with Docker

Follow these steps to run the application using Docker:

1. Make sure Docker is installed on your machine. You can download and install Docker from the official Docker   website (https://www.docker.com/get-started).

2. Build the Docker image:

   docker build -t contact-node-api.

3. Run the Docker container:

   docker run -p 3000:3000 contact-node-api.

4. Open your web browser and visit 'http://localhost:3000' to access the application.
